# Load / Performance Tests

This directory contains load testing scripts for the ResolveAgent platform.

## Tools

- [k6](https://k6.io/) for HTTP/gRPC load testing
- [locust](https://locust.io/) for Python-based load testing

## Usage

```bash
# k6 example
k6 run test/load/k6-api-benchmark.js

# locust example
locust -f test/load/locustfile.py --host=http://localhost:8080
```
